ActIndian Act
SubjectTootinaowaziibeeng Treaty Reserve ** Agreement **
PrecisOrder a) authorizing the Minister of Indian Affairs and Northern Development to enter into, on behalf of Her Majesty in Right of Canada, the TOOTINAOWAZIIBEENG TREATY RESERVE 1905 Railway Expropriation Settlement Agreement between Canada and the Tootinaowaziibeeng Treaty Reserve; and b) accepting the absolute surrender, of the lands described, pursuant to the Indian Act.
